Prevent a goblin raid
The Goblins plan a big raid on the village. A joint counterattack, carried out by the village soldiers and the brigands is already in preparation. The Goblins must be destroyed and their plans to attack the village thwarted.
#subobj  1
Meet the Lieutenant of the Chieftain
The meeting is supposed to take place where the road to the river leaves the valley between the hills. He should be alone and unarmed.
#subobj  2
Find the Goblins
The Goblins are gathering at the edge of the swamp not far from a high mountain resembling a pillar or a broken tooth. That mountain is the last one to the west, after it terrain becomes plainer.
#subobj  3
Kill the Goblins
The Goblin raid must be prevented by any means necessary.
